er on the route. The second little roof was fun, too.',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,1,'2013-07-28 - 050 - Gimli - IMG_1940.jpg',NULL,'https://lh5.googleusercontent.com/-6WB928SOvzM/Uhb18LxG3YI/AAAAAAACfJk/kReLBnWmA5E/s800/2013-07-28%252520-%252520050%252520-%252520Gimli%252520-%252520IMG_1940.jpg'),(28069,NULL,'https://lh5.googleusercontent.com/-lah6jXsV3YU/Uhb2C6H3jFI/AAAAAAACfJ0/p_CAX4lNDxM/s800/2013-07-28%252520-%252520053%252520-%252520Gimli%252520-%252520IMG_1943.jpg','Alec leading P2. ',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,1,'2013-07-28 - 053 - Gimli - IMG_1943.jpg',NULL,'https://lh5.googleusercontent.com/-lah6jXsV3YU/Uhb2C6H3jFI/AAAAAAACfJ0/p_CAX4lNDxM/s800/2013-07-28%252520-%252520053%252520-%252520Gimli%252520-%252520IMG_1943.jpg'),(28070,NULL,'https://lh4.googleusercontent.com/-r5dkQvxIduk/Uhb2G7dmoEI/AAAAAAACfKE/oK3-Fp0ZMxs/s800/2013-07-28%252520-%252520055%252520-%252520Gimli%252520-%252520IMG_1945.jpg','Alec leading P2. Unfortunately this pitch eased up in a hurry and was then mostly a scramble.',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,1,'2013-07-28 - 055 - Gimli - IMG_1945.jpg',NULL,'https://lh4.googleusercontent.com/-r5dkQvxIduk/Uhb2G7dmoEI/AAAAAAACfKE/oK3-Fp0ZMxs/s800/2013-07-28%252520-%252520055%252520-%252520Gimli%252520-%252520IMG_1945.jpg'),(28071,NULL,'https://lh4.googleusercontent.com/-KvXv3OUiWyk/Uhb2Lf4UY9I/AAAAAAACfKU/MGj0uCVYF_Y/s800/2013-07-28%252520-%252520057%252520-%252520Gimli%252520-%252520IMG_1948.jpg','Looking down P2. Getting some air!',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,1,'2013-07-28 - 057 - Gimli - IMG_1948.jpg',NULL,'https://lh4.googleusercontent.com/-KvXv3OUiWyk/Uhb2Lf4UY9I/AAAAAAACfKU/MGj0uCVYF_Y/s800/2013-07-28%252520-%252520057%252520-%252520Gimli%252520-%252520IMG_1948.jpg'),(28072,NULL,'https://lh5.googleusercontent.com/-tV5kD0g_NyY/Uhb2NNi--rI/AAAAAAACfKc/d4wBkCt1hdc/s800/2013-07-28%252520-%252520058%252520-%252520Gimli%252520-%252520IMG_1949.jpg','Alec on the comfy belay pedestal atop P2. I stepped across onto the face to lead P3.',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,1,'2