th, Middle, North)',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,1,'2013-07-30 - 023a - Pigeon Tower - IMG_2062.jpg',NULL,'https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/-uT3L3-aCqu4/Uht5dtXBAsI/AAAAAAACeMk/iXlEq52riSw/s800/2013-07-30%252520-%252520023a%252520-%252520Pigeon%252520Tower%252520-%252520IMG_2062.jpg'),(28190,NULL,'https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/-CJdqMBNDg6Q/Uht5iQay5MI/AAAAAAACeNQ/a11RFiFNBZs/s800/2013-07-30%252520-%252520024%252520-%252520Pigeon%252520Tower%252520-%252520IMG_2066.jpg','Climbers on the Vowell Glacier. This glacier was quite tame - Alec and I never felt the need to rope up, and an axe isn\'t even really needed! Crevasses are present, though, so certain conditions might warrant a rope, especially the bergschrund crossing for reaching the Bugaboo-Snowpatch Col.',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,1,'2013-07-30 - 024 - Pigeon Tower - IMG_2066.jpg',NULL,'https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/-CJdqMBNDg6Q/Uht5iQay5MI/AAAAAAACeNQ/a11RFiFNBZs/s800/2013-07-30%252520-%252520024%252520-%252520Pigeon%252520Tower%252520-%252520IMG_2066.jpg'),(28191,NULL,'https://lh4.googleusercontent.com/-PYcDHHU7WCk/Uht5-HIQvmI/AAAAAAACeRE/5MsJj8XfcOg/s800/2013-07-30%252520-%252520029a%252520-%252520Pigeon%252520Tower%252520-%252520IMG_2074.jpg','Pigeon Spire. The smaller spire below is called \'The Gooseneck\".',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,1,'2013-07-30 - 029a - Pigeon Tower - IMG_2074.jpg',NULL,'https://lh4.googleusercontent.com/-PYcDHHU7WCk/Uht5-HIQvmI/AAAAAAACeRE/5MsJj8XfcOg/s800/2013-07-30%252520-%252520029a%252520-%252520Pigeon%252520Tower%252520-%252520IMG_2074.jpg'),(28192,NULL,'https://lh4.googleusercontent.com/-lHk-RksHsXg/Uht6NC-Q3XI/AAAAAAACeTs/6-8BrQWt-Q8/s800/2013-07-30%252520-%252520034%252520-%252520Pigeon%252520Tower%252520-%252520IMG_2082.jpg','Panorama looking back towards Bugaboo-Snowpatch Col, with Alec following behind.',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,1,'2013-07-30 - 034 - Pigeon Tower - IMG_2082.jpg',NULL,'https://lh4.googleusercontent.com/-lHk-RksHsXg/Uht6NC-Q3XI/AAAAAAACeTs/6-8BrQWt-Q8/s800/2