 the first real pitch of the Great Dihedral. P7',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,1,'2013-07-31 - 020 - Beckey-Chouinard - IMG_2163.jpg',NULL,'https://lh6.googleusercontent.com/-GgQ-ZIHSP-s/Uht6mIoW_cI/AAAAAAACeXA/cD3wnQ_gMyc/s800/2013-07-31%252520-%252520020%252520-%252520Beckey-Chouinard%252520-%252520IMG_2163.jpg'),(28225,NULL,'https://lh5.googleusercontent.com/-5-6I6N30CBM/Uht6qbL4F9I/AAAAAAACeXg/9_mGUMzmPQY/s800/2013-07-31%252520-%252520021%252520-%252520Beckey-Chouinard%252520-%252520IMG_2164.jpg','Never ending corner on the Great Dihedral. P7',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,1,'2013-07-31 - 021 - Beckey-Chouinard - IMG_2164.jpg',NULL,'https://lh5.googleusercontent.com/-5-6I6N30CBM/Uht6qbL4F9I/AAAAAAACeXg/9_mGUMzmPQY/s800/2013-07-31%252520-%252520021%252520-%252520Beckey-Chouinard%252520-%252520IMG_2164.jpg'),(28226,NULL,'https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/-WQlYRopjokk/Uht6wQY-lmI/AAAAAAACeYI/-XIt-bF6fLY/s800/2013-07-31%252520-%252520022%252520-%252520Beckey-Chouinard%252520-%252520IMG_2166.jpg','Never ending corner on the Great Dihedral. P7',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,1,'2013-07-31 - 022 - Beckey-Chouinard - IMG_2166.jpg',NULL,'https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/-WQlYRopjokk/Uht6wQY-lmI/AAAAAAACeYI/-XIt-bF6fLY/s800/2013-07-31%252520-%252520022%252520-%252520Beckey-Chouinard%252520-%252520IMG_2166.jpg'),(28227,NULL,'https://lh5.googleusercontent.com/-qYSnTwXjARc/Uht61K9VgYI/AAAAAAACeY4/6FOmqzEmUWE/s800/2013-07-31%252520-%252520023%252520-%252520Beckey-Chouinard%252520-%252520IMG_2168.jpg','Looking down the Great Dihedral from just below the top. P7',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,1,'2013-07-31 - 023 - Beckey-Chouinard - IMG_2168.jpg',NULL,'https://lh5.googleusercontent.com/-qYSnTwXjARc/Uht61K9VgYI/AAAAAAACeY4/6FOmqzEmUWE/s800/2013-07-31%252520-%252520023%252520-%252520Beckey-Chouinard%252520-%252520IMG_2168.jpg'),(28228,NULL,'https://lh6.googleusercontent.com/-2pHSFiy2obo/Uht66Ca6j8I/AAAAAAACeZk/4DI1kO5Ur84/s800/2013-07-31%252520-%252520024%252520-%252520Beckey-Chouinard%252520-%25252