%2520-%25206.jpg','Final carryover day to get back to our camp at the Lower Saddle',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,1,'Teton Grand Slam - GE - 6.jpg',NULL,'https://lh5.googleusercontent.com/-wknsNckU7hs/UGGE0dbe-0I/AAAAAAABTvY/Em60IL10Or8/s800/Teton%2520Grand%2520Slam%2520-%2520GE%2520-%25206.jpg'),(29563,NULL,'https://lh4.googleusercontent.com/-XV7ZW3Lv080/UFfjhJP4MRI/AAAAAAABUvo/6dA4626ByEM/s800/2012-09-03%2520-%252001%2520-%2520Grand%2520Teton%2520under%2520morning%2520alpenglow%2520-%2520annotated.jpg','Grand Teton North Ridge, in its exposed position high on the Grand Teton',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,1,'2012-09-03 - 01 - Grand Teton under morning alpenglow - annotated.jpg',NULL,'https://lh4.googleusercontent.com/-XV7ZW3Lv080/UFfjhJP4MRI/AAAAAAABUvo/6dA4626ByEM/s800/2012-09-03%2520-%252001%2520-%2520Grand%2520Teton%2520under%2520morning%2520alpenglow%2520-%2520annotated.jpg'),(29564,NULL,'http://lh3.ggpht.com/-8DWCy9fCq7Q/UFGcb2GOtxI/AAAAAAABSyM/zrA5FZLONSg/s800/2012-09-04%252520-%25252001%252520-%252520Sunrise%252520over%252520Teewinot.jpg','Sunrise over Mt Teewinot.',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,1,'2012-09-04 - 01 - Sunrise over Teewinot.jpg',NULL,'http://lh3.ggpht.com/-8DWCy9fCq7Q/UFGcb2GOtxI/AAAAAAABSyM/zrA5FZLONSg/s800/2012-09-04%252520-%25252001%252520-%252520Sunrise%252520over%252520Teewinot.jpg'),(29565,NULL,'http://lh4.ggpht.com/-NEZlnW88Z9c/UFGccyWL1qI/AAAAAAABSyQ/JbmEyblkMmU/s800/2012-09-04%252520-%25252002%252520-%252520Sunrise%252520on%252520the%252520N%252520Ridge.jpg','Sunrise on the North Ridge, seen from camp.',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,1,'2012-09-04 - 02 - Sunrise on the N Ridge.jpg',NULL,'http://lh4.ggpht.com/-NEZlnW88Z9c/UFGccyWL1qI/AAAAAAABSyQ/JbmEyblkMmU/s800/2012-09-04%252520-%25252002%252520-%252520Sunrise%252520on%252520the%252520N%252520Ridge.jpg'),(29566,NULL,'http://lh6.ggpht.com/-_48kRebn2pY/UFGcgLhkDCI/AAAAAAABSyY/EZO926dV8nw/s800/2012-09-04%252520-%25252004%252520-%252520Climber%252520Cache.jpg','Help! I\'ve fallen and I can\'t get up!',NULL,NU