 by post-tensioning the system by telescoping the pole in order to reduce uplift on the compression member. The tent is rigid enough against longitudinal oscillations that no external out-of-plane restraints were necessary.:-)',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,1,'2012-09-05 - 01 - Tensegrity Tent System.jpg',NULL,'http://lh5.ggpht.com/-LCgpxA7IbSM/UFGdwJnf5mI/AAAAAAABS9g/QZUuF1MZOiY/s800/2012-09-05%252520-%25252001%252520-%252520Tensegrity%252520Tent%252520System.jpg'),(29823,NULL,'http://lh3.ggpht.com/-VwWcwWrQOO0/UFGd0JAB0gI/AAAAAAABS9o/yo5hn6UgJVc/s800/2012-09-05%252520-%25252003%252520-%252520Tensegrity%252520Tent%252520System.jpg','Connection detail of Tensegrity tent system to restrain it against the wind.',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,1,'2012-09-05 - 03 - Tensegrity Tent System.jpg',NULL,'http://lh3.ggpht.com/-VwWcwWrQOO0/UFGd0JAB0gI/AAAAAAABS9o/yo5hn6UgJVc/s800/2012-09-05%252520-%25252003%252520-%252520Tensegrity%252520Tent%252520System.jpg'),(29824,NULL,'https://lh5.googleusercontent.com/-rO9DFn7wJZM/UFRbSta6v4I/AAAAAAABUuI/In_yW1WVbqw/s800/2012-08-30%2520-%252044%2520-%2520Grand%2520Teton%2520from%2520Bonneys%2520Pinnacle%2520-%2520annotated.jpg','Lower Saddle Area and the first part of the Black Dike Traverse',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,1,'2012-08-30 - 44 - Grand Teton from Bonneys Pinnacle - annotated.jpg',NULL,'https://lh5.googleusercontent.com/-rO9DFn7wJZM/UFRbSta6v4I/AAAAAAABUuI/In_yW1WVbqw/s800/2012-08-30%2520-%252044%2520-%2520Grand%2520Teton%2520from%2520Bonneys%2520Pinnacle%2520-%2520annotated.jpg'),(29825,NULL,'http://lh5.ggpht.com/-BoYnAgrcTe8/UFqGjDpCPMI/AAAAAAABTDI/ZwqEGzygnVs/s800/2012-09-05%252520-%25252004%252520-%252520Steph%252520starting%252520the%252520Black%252520Dike%252520Traverse%252520-%252520annotated.jpg','Starting the Black Dike Traverse.',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,1,'2012-09-05 - 04 - Steph starting the Black Dike Traverse - annotated.jpg',NULL,'http://lh5.ggpht.com/-BoYnAgrcTe8/UFqGjDpCPMI/AAAAAAABTDI/ZwqEGzygnVs/s800/2012-09-05%252520-%2525